This module adds allergen information support to products in Odoo. Also
adds the posibility to show allergen icons on product labels without
barcodes. This is because labels with barcodes don't have enough space
to show allergens.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Configuration
=============

To configure this module:

1. To show allergens on product labels, go to *Settings > General
   Settings* and enable "Show Allergens on Product Labels"
2. Click on *Allergens* to create and manage allergens, this module
   comes with some predefined allergens
3. Go to product forms and add allergens in the Allergens tab

Usage
=====

This module allows you to:

- Define allergens with name and icon
- Associate allergens with product variants
- View allergens at product template level (computed from variants)
- Display allergen icons on product labels (configurable in settings)

Known issues / Roadmap
======================

``wkhtmltopdf`` currently has issues rendering SVG images correctly in
reports. SVG images are being preserved for a future improvement.

